description: Try our easy to follow Meat-Free Dim Sum recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Dumpling,Quick & easy dinner,Low saturated fat,Microwave,Christmas,Sweet potato,Low sugar,Low fat,Mushroom
name: Meat-Free Dim Sum Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: To make filling, combine ingredients in a small microwave-proof bowl and microwave on high for 2-3 minutes or until potato is soft. Mash and combine well.
Lay out the wonton wrappers on a clean work surface and brush with water to moisten.
Divide the filling into 24 portions and place centrally on each wrapper. Bring the corners of the wrapper together, to form a money bag shape, and seal the sides.

Meanwhile, bring a saucepan or wok of water to medium boil. Spray inside of a steamer with oil, add dim sum and steam on medium boil for 10 minutes or until cooked through. Garnish with coriander and serve with soy sauce.
